Rating: 4
When the September issue of Bon Appetit arrived this is the one recipe that jumped out at us. We've made a lot of risotto, in a number of ways, over the past 20 years. This has probably been our favorite to date. We prefer to make everything the same day, however as with most good risotto recipes, this is fairly labor intensive. You many want to take advantage of the hints about preparing some of it ahead of time. Don't save this special recipe for company - treat yourself and prepare it this weekend!

